Notes: UWO's 15th straight home win...UWO's seventh consecutive victory over UWSP...
UWSP trailed 36-16 at intermission after shooting just 25.9 percent (7-27)
from field in first half...UWO got a career-high 14 points off the bench from
Kolinski...UWO led 55-31 with 2:26 left in the third quarter.
Game.Officials: Erin Frias,  Tim Owens,  Matt Vanevenhoven
